Package: corevpn-server
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         adduser
Recommends: iptables | nftables
Suggests: corevpn-cli
Description: Secure OpenVPN-compatible VPN server with OAuth2 support
 CoreVPN is a modern, secure VPN server that provides:
  - Full OpenVPN protocol compatibility
  - OAuth2/OIDC/SAML authentication support
  - TLS 1.3 with modern cipher suites
  - Flexible connection logging with ghost mode
  - Web-based administration interface
 .
 This package contains the server component.

Package: corevpn-cli
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: corevpn-server
Description: Command-line client for CoreVPN
 CoreVPN is a modern, secure VPN server that provides OpenVPN
 protocol compatibility with modern authentication methods.
 .
 This package contains the command-line client for connecting
 to CoreVPN and OpenVPN servers.
